{"tid":1744633,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民間促區選表態 斷建制經濟鏈","createTime":"2019-11-22T00:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T00:50:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c41e79d150e67bb49a7a9de7b70c9581b7b4c21e","tid":1744633,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:05:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191122/35PFCFRAMVTEVMQVLWBB6SXGRE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191122%2F35PFCFRAMVTEVMQVLWBB6SXGRE%2F&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt87eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=8418e836\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191122%2F35PFCFRAMVTEVMQVLWBB6SXGRE%2F&h=7c45818a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191122/35PFCFRAMVTEVMQVLWBB6SXGRE/</a><br />\n<br />\n民間促區選表態 斷建制經濟鏈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191122/large/1574353242_4e96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191122%2Flarge%2F1574353242_4e96.jpg&h=ac28625c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民間記者會強調投票是抗爭其中一步，又指政府有責任確保選舉如期進行。何賢攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】區選後日舉行。民間記者會表示，選舉除是政治表態之外，亦可向國際反映港人堅持五大訴求，強調投票是抗爭運動其中一步，可割斷建制陣營經濟鏈。民間記者會發言人稱，現時香港面對人道災難，單單「血債票償」並不足夠，但區選有其重要性，除可反映港人不滿政府和北京干預外，勝選亦可割斷建制陣營經濟鏈，在國際戰線上可利用選舉結果，宣揚港人堅持五大訴求，故不能忽視選舉重要性，強調區選是抗爭運動其中一步，港人必須堅持，直至滿足五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「五大訴求要靠港人爭取」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警違《基本法》侵犯出入境自由<br />\n<br />\n對於有意見認為在區選前應暫停勇武抗爭，避免政府有藉口取消區選，發言人強調，政府沒任何藉口取消選舉，因投票權受《基本法》保障，確保選舉進行是政府責任。至於美國通過人權法，發言人認為法案對運動有正面影響，因抗爭者面對傷亡及被消失，法案可懲罰打壓人權自由的官員和監察香港人權狀況，有助保障抗爭者生命安全，但五大訴求依然要由港人自己爭取。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者在理大圍城中損失慘重，有人質疑死守違反流水抗爭策略，發言人表示，流水抗爭其中一個精粹，是在不同情況也尊重手足決定，支持理大抗爭者選擇，而事後網上已有針對性檢討，相信面對警暴政府，港人會繼續流水抗爭，直至達到五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n■記者于健民、曾偉龍"},{"pid":"c2d438bcdc31397c1dfd2fba76bada5340cea6d0","tid":1744633,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:07:28.000Z","msg":"熱狗、五毛：寧投建制 不投泛民, / 建議大家棄票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cda9eb14dde5ccfe691adc2a3b8949ea2481297","tid":1744633,"uid":115136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOY9fDG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpOY9fDG.jpg&h=ab06bbcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tuNBE5n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtuNBE5n.jpg&h=8f847821&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ZgKOYJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ZgKOYJ.jpg&h=e9a0a15f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZFvKw4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZFvKw4.jpg&h=1bfbba4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZJe06Lp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZJe06Lp.jpg&h=4ed091ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xco5yqq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXco5yqq.jpg&h=7c502b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z9t5yqr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9t5yqr.jpg&h=908a883d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w4hYTqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw4hYTqs.jpg&h=4589b464&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBKgE5s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBKgE5s.jpg&h=b03c9bf1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db54db3b47f73c05068bce26ea7be56bd54df4b4","tid":1744633,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cda9eb14dde5ccfe691adc2a3b8949ea2481297","tid":1744633,"uid":115136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https:/